long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The AgencyToolChest Chrome Extension is used to send information to the AgencyToolChest Web Application. Our tool allows you to easily input quote or policy information such as premium, quote type, and other fields from any page and at a click of a button, send this information to our web application and track your reports and visualize them with beautiful charts.
